videos.description: Kyle Alexander gets Tennessee on the board as he finishes a nice reverse layup surrounded by Arkansas' defenders.
videos.headline: Alexander finishes tough reverse lay-in

videos.description: Grant Williams escapes an Arkansas defender with a sick spin move and finishes with an easy floater in the lane for the Volunteers.
videos.headline: Williams' sweet spin move leads to easy finish for Tennessee

videos.description: Tennessee's Admiral Schofield gets free in transition and throws down a nice two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Schofield rises for 2-handed flush

videos.description: Arkansas' Jalen Harris comes up with a steal and flies for a nasty one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Harris gets up for powerful slam

videos.description: Tennessee turns defense to offense as Lamonte Turner gets a steal and takes it all the way for a easy 2-handed flush.
videos.headline: Turner skies for nice slam
